room_title: Escape room "Lost Teddy" by Trapped in Bismarck in Bismarck
room_address: 3333 E Broadway Ave., Suite 1219 Bismarck, ND 58501
room_description: Your parents have gone out for supper and left your uncle to babysit you. He loves playing tricks, so he has hidden your favorite teddy bear somewhere in your room. Your parents should arrive home in approximately 30 minutes. You have to find Teddy and get to bed before you're grounded!
